review_title: Good but the suction cup dont work well, Easy fix though read below.
reviews: I like how the product is easy to clean and all, but the only issue I have is that the suction cup dont work well on certain surfaces.. but figured out its a easy fix, all you need is some a little bit of super glue. Put a dab of it on the back of the suction cup and place it where you want it.. wait a few seconds and bam! it sticks without falling every 5 minutes! Only do this if you dont mind having a bit of superglue let behind on the wall when you remove it!

review_title: This mouse works way better than my dollarama one!
reviews: I bought a blue tooth one at dollarama and it lasted me for quite sometime but noticed it wouldent connect instantly and I had to remove it and reconnect it which was such a pain in the butt. I was going to buy a new one but figured I might as well look else where first. So I searched online and this came up! and let me tell you it was worth the the $9 as its pretty damn precise and accurate! Well worth the extra $6 compared to the dollarama version!

review_title: Great wallet if you prefer to just carry few cards around and few bills
reviews:
This wallet is perfect for minimalists as it as just enough card slots unlike some of the other wallets that have a unnecessary amount that make it overwhelming to find your cards while checking out. This wallet also has a little slot in the middle to store a few bills! great buy! Will update on how long it lasts

Update: The wallet only lasted me 5 months!
